### Backend

- Dev: `go run cmd/server/main.go`
- Migrations: `go run cmd/migrate/main.go up|down`
- Build: `go build -o server cmd/server/main.go`
- Quality: `go test ./...`, `go vet ./...`, `go fmt ./...`

### Frontend

- Dev: `cd frontend && pnpm dev`
- Build/Start: `pnpm build`, `pnpm start`
- Quality: `pnpm lint`, `pnpm format`, `pnpm check-types`

### Docker

- Dev stack: `docker-compose up -d`
- Logs: `docker-compose logs -f api`

See [CLAUDE.md](mdc:CLAUDE.md) for the full list and details.
